016package org.lifstools.jgoslin.parser;
017
018import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.Adduct;
019import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.Cycle;
020import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.Dictionary;
021import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.DoubleBonds;
022import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.Element;
023import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.FattyAcid;
024import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.FunctionalGroup;
025import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.Headgroup;
026import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.KnownFunctionalGroups;
027import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidAdduct;
028import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidException;
029import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidFaBondType;
030import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidLevel;
031import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidParsingException;
032import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.UnsupportedLipidException;
033import java.util.ArrayList;
034import java.util.HashMap;
035import java.util.Map;
036import static java.util.Map.entry;
037
038/**
039 * Event handler implementation for the {@link HmdbParser}.
040 *
041 * @author Dominik Kopczynski
042 * @author Nils Hoffmann
043 */
044public class HmdbParserEventHandler extends LipidBaseParserEventHandler {
045
046    private int dbPositions;
047    private String dbCistrans;
048    private Dictionary furan = null;
049
050    /**
051     * Create a new {@code HmdbParserEventHandler}.
052     *
053     * @param knownFunctionalGroups the known functional groups
054     */
055    public HmdbParserEventHandler(KnownFunctionalGroups knownFunctionalGroups) {
056        super(knownFunctionalGroups);
057        try {
058            registeredEvents = Map.ofEntries(
059                    entry("lipid_pre_event", this::resetParser),
060                    entry("lipid_post_event", this::buildLipid),
061                    // set adduct events
062                    entry("adduct_info_pre_event", this::newAdduct),
063                    entry("adduct_pre_event", this::addAdduct),
064                    entry("charge_pre_event", this::addCharge),
065                    entry("charge_sign_pre_event", this::addChargeSign),
066                    entry("fa_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
067                    entry("gl_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
068                    entry("gl_molecular_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
069                    entry("mediator_pre_event", this::mediatorEvent),
070                    entry("gl_mono_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
071                    entry("pl_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
072                    entry("pl_three_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
073                    entry("pl_four_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
074                    entry("sl_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
075                    entry("st_species_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
076                    entry("st_sub1_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
077                    entry("st_sub2_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
078                    entry("ganglioside_names_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
079                    entry("fa_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
080                    entry("gl_molecular_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),
081                    entry("unsorted_fa_separator_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),
082                    entry("fa2_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),
083                    entry("fa3_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),
084                    entry("fa4_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),
085                    entry("db_single_position_pre_event", this::setIsomericLevel),
086                    entry("db_single_position_post_event", this::addDbPosition),
087                    entry("db_position_number_pre_event", this::addDbPositionNumber),
088                    entry("cistrans_pre_event", this::addCistrans),
089                    entry("lcb_pre_event", this::newLcb),
090                    entry("lcb_post_event", this::cleanLcb),
091                    entry("fa_pre_event", this::newFa),
092                    entry("fa_post_event", this::appendFa),
093                    entry("ether_pre_event", this::addEther),
094                    entry("hydroxyl_pre_event", this::addHydroxyl),
095                    entry("db_count_pre_event", this::addDoubleBonds),
096                    entry("carbon_pre_event", this::addCarbon),
097                    entry("fa_lcb_suffix_type_pre_event", this::addOneHydroxyl),
098                    entry("interlink_fa_pre_event", this::interlinkFa),
099                    entry("lipid_suffix_pre_event", this::lipidSuffix),
100                    entry("methyl_pre_event", this::addMethyl),
101                    entry("furan_fa_pre_event", this::furanFa),
102                    entry("furan_fa_post_event", this::furanFaPost),
103                    entry("furan_fa_mono_pre_event", this::furanFaMono),
104                    entry("furan_fa_di_pre_event", this::furanFaDi),
105                    entry("furan_first_number_pre_event", this::furanFaFirstNumber),
106                    entry("furan_second_number_pre_event", this::furanFaSecondNumber)
107            );
108        } catch (Exception e) {
109            throw new LipidParsingException("Cannot initialize LipidMapsParserEventHandler.");
110        }
111    }
112
113    @Override
114    protected void resetParser(TreeNode node) {
115        content = null;
116        level = LipidLevel.FULL_STRUCTURE;
117        headGroup = "";
118        lcb = null;
119        adduct = null;
120        faList.clear();
121        currentFa = null;
122        useHeadGroup = false;
123        dbPositions = 0;
124        dbCistrans = "";
125        furan = new Dictionary();
126        headgroupDecorators.clear();
127    }
128
129    private void setIsomericLevel(TreeNode node) {
130        dbPositions = 0;
131        dbCistrans = "";
132    }
133
134    private void addDbPosition(TreeNode node) {
135        if (currentFa != null) {
136            currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(dbPositions, dbCistrans);
137            if (!dbCistrans.equals("E") && !dbCistrans.equals("Z")) {
138                setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
139            }
140        }
141    }
142
143    private void addDbPositionNumber(TreeNode node) {
144        dbPositions = node.getInt();
145    }
146
147    private void addCistrans(TreeNode node) {
148        dbCistrans = node.getText();
149    }
150
151    private void setHeadGroupName(TreeNode node) {
152        headGroup = node.getText();
153    }
154
155    private void setSpeciesLevel(TreeNode node) {
156        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SPECIES);
157    }
158
159    private void setMolecularLevel(TreeNode node) {
160        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.MOLECULAR_SPECIES);
161    }
162
163    private void mediatorEvent(TreeNode node) {
164        useHeadGroup = true;
165        headGroup = node.getText();
166    }
167
168    private void newFa(TreeNode node) {
169        currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", knownFunctionalGroups);
170    }
171
172    private void newLcb(TreeNode node) {
173        lcb = new FattyAcid("LCB", knownFunctionalGroups);
174        lcb.setType(LipidFaBondType.LCB_REGULAR);
175        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
176        currentFa = lcb;
177    }
178
179    private void cleanLcb(TreeNode node) {
180        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) {
181            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
182        }
183        currentFa = null;
184    }
185
186    private void appendFa(TreeNode node) {
187        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() < 0) {
188            throw new LipidException("Double bond count does not match with number of double bond positions");
189        }
190        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) {
191            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
192        }
193
194        faList.add(currentFa);
195        currentFa = null;
196    }
197
198    private void buildLipid(TreeNode node) {
199        if (lcb != null) {
200            faList.add(0, lcb);
201        }
202
203        Headgroup headgroup = prepareHeadgroupAndChecks();
204
205        LipidAdduct lipid = new LipidAdduct(assembleLipid(headgroup), adduct);
206        content = lipid;
207    }
208
209    private void addEther(TreeNode node) {
210        String ether = node.getText();
211        if (ether.equals("O-") || ether.equals("o-")) {
212            currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMANYL);
213        } else if (ether.equals("P-")) {
214            currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMENYL);
215        } else {
216            throw new UnsupportedLipidException("Fatty acyl chain of type '" + ether + "' is currently not supported");
217        }
218    }
219
220    private void addHydroxyl(TreeNode node) {
221        String old_hydroxyl = node.getText();
222        int num_h = 0;
223        if (old_hydroxyl.equals("d")) {
224            num_h = 2;
225        } else if (old_hydroxyl.equals("t")) {
226            num_h = 3;
227        }
228
229        if (spRegularLcb()) {
230            num_h -= 1;
231        }
232
233        FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
234        functional_group.setCount(num_h);
235        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
236            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
237        }
238        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
239    }
240
241    private void addMethyl(TreeNode node) {
242        FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("Me");
243        functional_group.setPosition(currentFa.getNumCarbon() - (node.getText().equals("i-") ? 1 : 2));
244        currentFa.setNumCarbon(currentFa.getNumCarbon() - 1);
245
246        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("Me")) {
247            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("Me", new ArrayList<>());
248        }
249        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("Me").add(functional_group);
250    }
251
252    private void addOneHydroxyl(TreeNode node) {
253        if (currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH") && currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").get(0).getPosition() == -1) {
254            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").get(0).setCount(currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").get(0).getCount() + 1);
255        } else {
256            FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
257            if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
258                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
259            }
260            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
261        }
262    }
263
264    private void addDoubleBonds(TreeNode node) {
265        currentFa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(node.getInt());
266    }
267
268    private void addCarbon(TreeNode node) {
269        currentFa.setNumCarbon(currentFa.getNumCarbon() + node.getInt());
270    }
271
272    private void furanFa(TreeNode node) {
273        furan = new Dictionary();
274    }
275
276    private void furanFaPost(TreeNode node) {
277        int l = 4 + (int) furan.get("len_first") + (int) furan.get("len_second");
278        currentFa.setNumCarbon(l);
279
280        int start = 1 + (int) furan.get("len_first");
281        int end = 3 + start;
282        DoubleBonds cyclo_db = new DoubleBonds(2);
283        cyclo_db.getDoubleBondPositions().put(start, "E");
284        cyclo_db.getDoubleBondPositions().put(2 + start, "E");
285
286        HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> cyclo_fg = new HashMap<>();
287        cyclo_fg.put("Me", new ArrayList<>());
288
289        if (((String) furan.get("type")).equals("m")) {
290            FunctionalGroup fg = knownFunctionalGroups.get("Me");
291            fg.setPosition(1 + start);
292            cyclo_fg.get("Me").add(fg);
293        } else if (((String) furan.get("type")).equals("d")) {
294            FunctionalGroup fg = knownFunctionalGroups.get("Me");
295            fg.setPosition(1 + start);
296            cyclo_fg.get("Me").add(fg);
297            fg = knownFunctionalGroups.get("Me");
298            fg.setPosition(2 + start);
299            cyclo_fg.get("Me").add(fg);
300        }
301
302        ArrayList<Element> bridge_chain = new ArrayList<>();
303        bridge_chain.add(Element.O);
304        Cycle cycle = new Cycle(end - start + 1 + bridge_chain.size(), start, end, cyclo_db, cyclo_fg, bridge_chain, knownFunctionalGroups);
305        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("cy", new ArrayList<>());
306        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("cy").add(cycle);
307    }
308
309    private void furanFaMono(TreeNode node) {
310        furan.put("type", "m");
311    }
312
313    private void furanFaDi(TreeNode node) {
314        furan.put("type", "d");
315    }
316
317    private void furanFaFirstNumber(TreeNode node) {
318        furan.put("len_first", node.getInt());
319    }
320
321    private void furanFaSecondNumber(TreeNode node) {
322        furan.put("len_second", node.getInt());
323    }
324
325    private void interlinkFa(TreeNode node) {
326        throw new UnsupportedLipidException("Interconnected fatty acyl chains are currently not supported");
327    }
328
329    private void lipidSuffix(TreeNode node) {
330        //throw new UnsupportedLipidException("Lipids with suffix '" + node.getText() + "' are currently not supported");
331    }
332
333    private void newAdduct(TreeNode node) {
334        if (adduct == null) adduct = new Adduct("", "");
335    }
336
337    private void addAdduct(TreeNode node) {
338        adduct.setAdductString(node.getText());
339    }
340
341    private void addCharge(TreeNode node) {
342        adduct.setCharge(Integer.valueOf(node.getText()));
343    }
344
345    private void addChargeSign(TreeNode node) {
346        String sign = node.getText();
347        if (sign.equals("+")) {
348            adduct.setChargeSign(1);
349        } else if (sign.equals("-")) {
350            adduct.setChargeSign(-1);
351        }
352        if (adduct.getCharge() == 0) adduct.setCharge(1);
353    }
354}
